Thanks for your offer to assist @kmalakoff !

@andydavis1 and @suharshs have been slowly chugging along gradients in C++ (using the [`REGISTER_OP_GRADIENT`](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/4172ca2cd7ac34be67bda2600944d284e8907b95/tensorflow/core/framework/function.h#L423) macro). The broad plan is to (1) have gradients for every op registered in C++, (2) Add a C API call equivalent of `tf.gradients` that uses these.

@andydavis1 or @suharshs might have suggestions on the most effective way for you to contribute towards this.
